WEBVTT

00:12.279 --> 00:18.117
<i>Love is a song that never ends</i>

00:18.118 --> 00:23.789
<i>Life may be swift and fleeting</i>

00:23.790 --> 00:29.295
<i>Hope may die
Yet love's beautiful music</i>

00:29.296 --> 00:35.200
<i>Comes each day like the dawn</i>

00:35.201 --> 00:40.906
<i>Love is a song that never ends</i>

00:40.907 --> 00:46.512
<i>One simple theme repeating</i>

00:46.513 --> 00:52.284
<i>Like the voice of a heavenly choir</i>

00:52.285 --> 00:59.703
<i>Love's sweet music flows on</i>

01:06.032 --> 01:12.438
<i>Like the voice of a heavenly choir</i>

01:12.439 --> 01:19.521
<i>Love's sweet music flows on</i>

03:21.367 --> 03:24.136
Hoo!

03:26.105 --> 03:28.473
Hoo-hoo, hoo, hoo.

03:30.543 --> 03:32.147
Hoo-hoo!

04:49.489 --> 04:52.950
- Wake up! Wake up!
- Oh, what now?

04:52.951 --> 04:56.862
- Wake up, Friend Owl.
- Hey, what's going on around here?

04:56.863 --> 04:59.531
- Wake up!
- It's happened. It's happened.

04:59.532 --> 05:01.500
The new prince is born.

05:01.501 --> 05:05.448
- We're going to see him.
- Come on. You better hurry up.

05:16.316 --> 05:20.730
Oh. Well, look.

05:23.623 --> 05:26.626
- Well.
- Isn't he cute?

05:26.926 --> 05:28.393
Oh...

05:28.394 --> 05:32.967
Well... this is quite an occasion.

05:33.466 --> 05:37.914
Yes, sir, it isn't every
day a prince is born.

05:38.971 --> 05:41.140
You're to be congratulated.

05:41.141 --> 05:43.210
- Yes, congratulations.
- Congratulations.

05:43.211 --> 05:47.213
- Congratulations.
- Thank you very much.

05:47.847 --> 05:52.056
Come on. Wake up.
We have company.

05:57.123 --> 05:59.091
Hello. Hello, there.

05:59.092 --> 06:02.061
- Hello, little prince.
- Hello. Hello, there.

06:02.062 --> 06:04.563
Hello, little prince.

06:04.564 --> 06:07.066
Hoo-hoo!

06:07.767 --> 06:09.401
Hoo-hoo!

06:10.027 --> 06:12.064
Hoo-hoo!

06:22.315 --> 06:26.228
Look! He's trying to get up.

06:48.574 --> 06:50.909
Kinda wobbly, isn't he?

06:50.910 --> 06:53.412
Thumper!

06:54.046 --> 06:56.548
Well, he is.

06:57.984 --> 07:00.226
Aren't you?

07:07.160 --> 07:10.937
Looks to me like he's
getting kind of sleepy.

07:13.733 --> 07:16.134
I think it's time we all left.

07:16.135 --> 07:20.338
Come on. Shoo-shoo! Psst!
Come on. Shoo-shoo!

07:20.339 --> 07:22.441
Psst!

07:25.378 --> 07:27.480
Psst!

07:35.354 --> 07:38.562
Thumper. Come on.

07:41.060 --> 07:43.665
Whatcha gonna call him?

07:43.796 --> 07:48.133
Well... I think I'll
call him Bambi.

07:48.134 --> 07:50.443
Bambi.

07:51.971 --> 07:55.140
Yep, I guess that'll do all right.

07:55.141 --> 07:57.643
Bambi.

07:58.077 --> 08:00.579
My little Bambi.

08:30.109 --> 08:33.556
Walking already. Well,
what do you know.

08:49.695 --> 08:52.531
- Good morning.
- Good morning, Mrs Quail.

08:52.532 --> 08:56.536
And where's the young
prince this mo... Oh!

08:57.904 --> 09:01.951
- Good morning, Bambi.
- Good morning, young prince.

09:04.677 --> 09:07.179
Goodbye.

09:09.749 --> 09:12.251
Good morning, young prince.

09:18.324 --> 09:20.826
Good morning, young prince.

09:34.740 --> 09:37.242
Good morning. Hm.

09:37.910 --> 09:40.412
Nice sunny day.

09:51.824 --> 09:54.225
- What's the matter?
- What happened?

09:54.226 --> 09:57.028
Did the young prince fall down?

09:57.029 --> 10:00.942
- Is he hurt?
- No, he's all right.

10:02.335 --> 10:04.970
He doesn't walk very good, does he?

10:04.971 --> 10:07.473
Thumper.

10:07.974 --> 10:10.476
Yes, Mama?

10:10.610 --> 10:14.189
What did your father
tell you this morning?

10:16.616 --> 10:20.422
If you can't say something nice...

10:23.122 --> 10:26.660
don't say nothing at all.

10:27.727 --> 10:31.596
Come on, Bambi, get up. Try again.

10:31.597 --> 10:34.633
Come on, get up. Get up, Bambi.

10:34.634 --> 10:37.136
- Get up.
- Try again.

11:07.933 --> 11:12.037
I'm thumping. That's why
they call me Thumper.

11:12.038 --> 11:14.848
...call me Thumper.

11:14.940 --> 11:17.442
- Thumper!
- Thumper!

11:34.593 --> 11:38.199
Come on. You can do it.

11:38.564 --> 11:42.136
Hop over it. Like this.

11:42.968 --> 11:45.948
- Hop over it.
- Hop over it.

11:48.374 --> 11:50.876
Like this.

12:02.888 --> 12:05.834
You didn't hop far enough.

12:08.461 --> 12:11.498
That's it. Now the other one.

12:21.440 --> 12:24.743
Gee whiz, what happened that time?

12:42.828 --> 12:45.330
Those are birds.

12:46.599 --> 12:48.500
Bur.

12:48.501 --> 12:50.034
Bur!

12:50.035 --> 12:52.776
Look, he's trying to talk.

12:52.938 --> 12:54.706
Bur!

12:54.707 --> 12:57.209
He's trying to say "bird".

12:59.078 --> 13:01.580
Say "bird".

13:02.047 --> 13:04.549
Bur.

13:04.683 --> 13:06.551
Bird.

13:06.552 --> 13:08.827
Bur.

13:09.121 --> 13:10.989
Uh-uh.

13:10.990 --> 13:12.957
Bird.

13:12.958 --> 13:15.460
Come on, say "bird", say "bird".

13:15.461 --> 13:18.530
Say "bird". Say "bird".
Come on, say "bird".

13:18.531 --> 13:21.033
Say "bird".

13:22.668 --> 13:24.202
Bird!

13:26.272 --> 13:29.407
He talked! He talked!
He talked, Mama.

13:29.408 --> 13:31.910
The young prince said "bird".

13:31.911 --> 13:35.324
Bird, bird, bird,
bird, bird, bird...

13:54.266 --> 13:55.667
Bird!

13:55.668 --> 13:57.936
No, that's not a bird.

13:57.937 --> 14:00.271
That's a butterfly.

14:00.272 --> 14:02.440
Butterfly?

14:02.441 --> 14:04.318
Butter...

14:08.347 --> 14:10.215
Butterfly.

14:10.216 --> 14:12.817
No, that's a flower.

14:12.818 --> 14:17.061
- Flower?
- Uh-huh, it's pretty.

14:21.827 --> 14:23.962
Purty.

14:30.970 --> 14:32.871
Flower!

14:32.872 --> 14:34.439
Me?

14:39.979 --> 14:42.652
No, no.

14:43.082 --> 14:45.550
That's not a flower.

14:45.551 --> 14:48.286
- He's a little...
- Oh, that's all right.

14:48.287 --> 14:53.600
He can call me a
flower if he wants to.

14:57.363 --> 15:00.673
I don't mind.

15:03.836 --> 15:06.839
Purty! Purty flower!

15:08.874 --> 15:10.645
Oh...

15:12.912 --> 15:14.914
gosh.

15:25.791 --> 15:29.761
I think I better go home now.

