<i>You come along
With your pretty little song</i>

17:14.700 --> 17:17.135
<i>- Gay little roundelay
- Gay little roundelay</i>

17:17.136 --> 17:19.604
<i>- Song of the rainy day
- Song of the rainy day</i>

17:19.605 --> 17:22.307
<i>How I love to hear your patter
Pretty little pitter-patter.</i>

